<br>
I am lev 47 now, and am looking for a way to get some more xp. because of the time i play it is usually extra hard to get a group. (european time zone). The only AoE spell i can use as far as i know is Gravity Flux and maybe some circle. <br>
<br>
Also what will be the best place to practise this?<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/4/01 6:02:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What spells to use when quad kiting</span><hr size=1> You need 3 spells:<br>
<br>
1. Circle of Force (lvl 34 AE nuke)<br>
2. Bonds of Force (lvl 29 AE snare)<br>
3. Spirit of Wolf (just buy potions or get Jboots)<br>
<br>
